==English==
===Noun===
'''chestnut''' (''plural'' '''chestnuts''')

#A smooth-shelled [[nut]] of a tree or shrub of the genus ''Castanea''.
#A [[tree]] that bears chestnuts.
#A [[red]]dish-[[brown]] [[colour]]/color.
#A reddish-brown [[horse]].
#The [[wood]] of a chestnut tree.

